      "beat_id": "B01",
      "estimated_duration_s": 10,
      "narration_text": "This is Liam, in for Bear. Prepare every spin one-half particle as definitely up along z. Measure sideways along x, then measure z again. Half of the final results are now down.",
      "shot": {
